# ---- uv ----
# uv.lock is uv's lockfile. Source of truth for deps currently lives in
# requirements/*.txt, so the lockfile derived from an empty pyproject.toml
# is noise. Re-include this file when we migrate deps into pyproject.toml.
uv.lock

